{"id": 2829, "genre": 1000, "title": "现如今，你觉得哪些东西正在变成奢侈品？", "description": "那些以往不以为意如今越来越难得到的东西还有啥，请尽情在留言区补充。", "record_count": 21600, "comment_count": 75, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190307172424peDX3HQ0JRsSa9uy.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-03-07T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 5467, "title": "现如今，你觉得哪些东西正在变成奢侈品？", "content": "现如今，你觉得哪些东西正在变成奢侈品？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 331808, "content": "学纯文科专业，“毕业即失业、马上要被人工智能替代”", "image": "img/option/option/20190307172634jU7FOPnXrSdV4QRz.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 331811, "content": "“纯粹”友谊，人际关系谁还不讲究个投入产出比", "image": "img/option/option/20190307172759I3RcfE0zv4NWt6Tx.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 331812, "content": "室外运动，没被占的场地和没雾霾的天气都可遇不可求", "image": "img/option/option/20190307173248fe5smGVSh8r2nBTA.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 331813, "content": "自知之明，看到满屏幕的成功案例总觉得自己也行", "image": "img/option/option/20190307173332SnbuoiVreNPB3k1Z.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 331815, "content": "行动力，问题看得都很清楚就是不愿意行动", "image": "img/option/option/20190307173525e0MYkA2D9OUpzdHN.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 331817, "content": "无所事事，越来越无法坦然地享受啥都不干", "image": "img/option/option/20190307173701jPizbvBue7yhO4EG.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 331818, "content": "隐私，总是刚想买个啥，下一分钟就看到对应的广告了", "image": "img/option/option/20190307173827M1htJVX6UbCgkw35.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 331819, "content": "用词自由，稍有不慎就“政治不正确”了", "image": "img/option/option/20190307173921NWnwy8bLjvqPJ5O2.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}